===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro}} {{term|dromadaire|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|LL.}} {{term|dromedarius||kind of camel|lang=la}}, from Classical {{etyl|la}} {{term|dromas|dromas, dromadis|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc}} {{term|δρομάς κάμηλος||tr=dromas kamelos|running camel|lang=grc}}, from {{term|δρόμος|tr=dromos||race course|lang=grc}}.

